OL,3,CHow could Labour's new workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation impact you?
OL,6,FThe government have announced a raft
OL,7,Fof changes to their landmark workers'
OL,8,Frights legislation, a bill which they
OL,9,Fsay marks a "generational change".
OL,11,FThe controversial legislation has been
OL,12,Fwatered down since Labour first
OL,13,Fannounced the plans before the
OL,14,Felection, but on Tuesday a number of
OL,15,Famendments have been brought in to
OL,16,Fgive workers more robust rights before
OL,17,Fthe bill enters it's final stages next
OL,18,Fweek.
