OL,3,CHow could Labour's new workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation impact you?
OL,6,FUnions had been concerned companies
OL,7,Fwould use agency workers to get round
OL,8,Fthe ban on "exploitative" zero-hours
OL,9,Fcontracts.
OL,11,FDespite previously promising to ban
OL,12,Fzero-hours contracts entirely, before
OL,13,Fthe election Labour watered down the
OL,14,Fpledge to add in the word
OL,15,F"exploitative", allowing some workers
OL,16,Fto opt to stay on zero hours.
OL,18,FStatutory sick pay becomes a legal
OL,19,Fright for all workers
