OL,3,CHow could Labour's new workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation impact you?
OL,6,FThe government are also extending sick
OL,7,Fpay to workers earning under #123 a
OL,8,Fweek from day one of their illness.
OL,9,FStaff will be paid 80% of their
OL,10,Faverage weekly earning or #116.75
OL,11,Fstatutory sick pay, whichever is
OL,12,Flowest.
OL,14,FAt the moment, workers must be off
OL,15,Fwork sick for three days in a row to
OL,16,Fqualify for statutory sick pay.
