OL,3,CHow could Labour's new workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation impact you?
OL,6,FOne area of the bill that has been
OL,7,Fwatered down for employees are plans
OL,8,Fto give people the "right to switch
OL,9,Foff".
OL,11,FLabour had promised to make it illegal
OL,12,Ffor companies to expect workers to be
OL,13,Fcontactable outside their working
OL,14,Fhours, but that pledge has now been
OL,15,Fdropped after concerns from businesses.
