OL,4,Clegislation impact you?
OL,6,FWhen asked on Tuesday about the plans
OL,7,Fbeing dropped, Rayner suggested the
OL,8,Fgovernment will "deal with" the issue
OL,9,Fin a "statutory code", but media
OL,10,Fbriefings by government sources
OL,11,Fsuggest the commitment has been
OL,12,Fscrapped entirely.
