OL,3,CHow could Labour's new workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation impact you?
OL,6,FWhen the government first outlined the
OL,7,Fbill, they already promised they would
OL,8,Fbe banning most fire and rehire
OL,9,Fpractices, but an amendment today
OL,10,Fdoubles the penalties companies can
OL,11,Fface if they use fire and rehire.
OL,13,FCompanies could now be forced to pay
OL,14,Fthe worker they have fired and rehired
OL,15,F180 days' worth of pay in
OL,16,Fcompensation, which is double the
OL,17,Fcurrent 90-day penalty payment.
OL,19,FExpanding bereavement leave to couples
OL,20,Fwho have a miscarriage before 24 weeks
