OL,3,CHow could Labour's new workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation impact you?
OL,6,FThe changes could also give parents
OL,7,Fthe right to two weeks bereavement
OL,8,Fleave if they have a miscarriage
OL,9,Fbefore 24 weeks gestation. Under
OL,10,Fcurrent rules parents could only get
OL,11,Fbereavement leave after 24 weeks.
OL,13,FMany companies and organisations
OL,14,Falready offer this, but the plans will
OL,15,Fmake it a universal right in England,
OL,16,FWales and Scotland.
