OL,3,CHow could Labour's new workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation impact you?
OL,6,FSome of the other changes include
OL,7,Fadapting the way employees can get
OL,8,Ftrade union recognition and the way
OL,9,Findustrial action is staged.
OL,11,FCurrently workers have to give 14 days
OL,12,Fnotice to stage industrial action, but
OL,13,Fthat will be lowered to ten.
OL,15,FThe government will also have the
OL,16,Fpower to lower threshold at which
OL,17,Femployees can ballot for union
OL,18,Frecognition - it's currently 10%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
