OL,3,CHow could Labour's new workers' rights
OL,4,Clegislation impact you?
OL,6,FThe length of time before a mandate
OL,7,Ffor industrial action expires will
OL,8,Falso increase from six to 12 months.
OL,10,FUmbrella companies will also now be
OL,11,Fregulated by the government over their
OL,12,Femployment rights under the changes.
